{"title":"ofctlrest","uid":"d05d6aa215cd9c39136c0b44f181dfe8","slug":"ofctlrest","date":"2022-07-18T03:52:22.000Z","updated":"2022-07-18T03:58:15.866Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ofctlrest.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"ryu-app-ofctl-rest\"><a href=\"#ryu-app-ofctl-rest\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ryu.app.ofctl_rest\"></a>ryu.app.ofctl_rest</h1><p>ryu.app.ofctl_rest provides REST APIs for retrieving the switch stats and Updating the switch stats. This application helps you debug your application and get various statistics.</p>\n<p>【其实就是ryu自己提供的一个应用程序，提供了获取交换机状态以及更新交换机状态的REST APIs。该应用可以帮助我们debug自己创建的应用并获取各种统计数据】</p>\n \n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"/post/ofctlrest.htm/1.png\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n<p>This application supports OpenFlow version 1.0, 1.2, 1.3, 1.4 and 1.5.</p>\n<p>【支持OpenFlow版本 1.0 1.2 1.3 1.4和1.5】</p>\n<h2 id=\"使用\"><a href=\"#使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用\"></a>使用</h2><ol>\n<li>将ofctl_rest和simple_switch_13.py一起启动</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/post/ofctlrest.htm/2.png\" alt=\"2\"></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>启动拓扑</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/post/ofctlrest.htm/3.png\" alt=\"3\"></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>另起一个终端，进行请求发送，测试接口</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"/post/ofctlrest.htm/4.png\" alt=\"4\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>其余接口尚未测试，该接口响应成功，响应结果是否正确要看具体实验情况。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"【注】\"><a href=\"#【注】\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"【注】\"></a>【注】</h2><p>使用的是python3，则需要修改ofctl_rest源码：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>第133行：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\">#原本</span>\nbody<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>json<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dumps<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dps<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#改为</span>\nbody <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> json<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dumps<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dps<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>encode<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"utf-8\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>若是python2，则应该不需要修改，运行时不会报错</li>\n</ul>\n","feature":true,"text":"ryu.app.ofctl_restryu.app.ofctl_rest provides REST APIs for retrieving the switch stats and Updating the switch stats. This application help...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":646,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ryu-app-ofctl-rest\"><span class=\"toc-text\">ryu.app.ofctl_rest</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">使用</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E3%80%90%E6%B3%A8%E3%80%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">【注】</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"LiuQuanZe","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"a good guy!","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Console失效","uid":"85d7f0ee0105da9c47f8cfa58c2659ee","slug":"CannotUseConsole","date":"2022-07-19T08:02:42.000Z","updated":"2022-07-19T08:10:36.039Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CannotUseConsole.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"console.log()失效问题描述：当使用console.log()想要打印到控制台时，发现idea出现下滑红线，并且num run serve也通不过。 错误信息：ESLint: Unexpected console statement.(no-console) 解决办法：...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount